name: Eloise Wool Moroccan Washable
long_description:
Luxurious, machine-washable, and made by hand, Rugs USA’s Washable Wool rugs are poised to take center stage in your home. Not only are they undeniably plush and beautiful, with a soft and substantial pile that invites you to slip off your shoes and relax—they are made in one piece, and resistant to spills, stains, kids, pets, and any smudge that comes your way. And when the unavoidable “oops” happens during a lively cocktail party or slime-making session, you can breathe a sigh of relief: when the party’s over, simply roll up your rug and run it through the washing machine!
Made from sustainably-sourced premium hand-made wool, our washable rugs help define what it means to live your best life at home. Enjoying your space worry- and stress-free – we’ve got your floors covered.

Make the Most of Your Washable Wool Rug
Easy to set up: When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made in one piece, with no separate backing.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.
Add a rug pad: If you want to add a more plush feel underfoot and anchor the rug to the floor, layer a Rugs USA rug pad underneath the rug.
Cleans easily: Vacuum carefully with the brush on its highest setting. Machine wash the rug in cold water and a gentle cycle. Do not use bleach. Low tumble dry. Never wring. Wash only periodically to help prevent shredding of fibers. Low heat iron when need.

name: Mona Pinstriped Sunset Wool Washable
long_description:
Luxurious, machine-washable, and made by hand, Rugs USA’s Washable Wool rugs are poised to take center stage in your home. Not only are they undeniably plush and beautiful, with a soft and substantial pile that invites you to slip off your shoes and relax—they are made in one piece, and resistant to spills, stains, kids, pets, and any smudge that comes your way. And when the unavoidable “oops” happens during a lively cocktail party or slime-making session, you can breathe a sigh of relief: when the party’s over, simply roll up your rug and run it through the washing machine!
Made from sustainably-sourced premium hand-made wool, our washable rugs help define what it means to live your best life at home. Enjoying your space worry- and stress-free – we’ve got your floors covered.

Make the Most of Your Washable Wool Rug
Easy to set up: When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made in one piece, with no separate backing.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.
Add a rug pad: If you want to add a more plush feel underfoot and anchor the rug to the floor, layer a Rugs USA rug pad underneath the rug.
Cleans easily: Vacuum carefully with the brush on its highest setting. Machine wash the rug in cold water and a gentle cycle. Do not use bleach. Low tumble dry. Never wring. Wash only periodically to help prevent shredding of fibers. Low heat iron when need.

Easy to set up: When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.

One-piece design: Our washable rugs have an integrated non-slip backing, which eliminates the hassle of needing a separate backing layer. When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.

Make the Most of Your Washable Wool Rug
Easy to set up: When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.

Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.

Cleans easily: Vacuum carefully with the brush on its highest setting. Machine wash the rug in cold water and a gentle cycle. Do not use bleach. Low tumble dry. Never wring. Wash only periodically to help prevent shredding of fibers. Low heat iron when need.

name: Rhea Wool Washable
long_description:
Luxurious, machine-washable, and made by hand, Rugs USA’s Washable Wool rugs are poised to take center stage in your home. Not only are they undeniably plush and beautiful, with a soft and substantial pile that invites you to slip off your shoes and relax—they are made in one piece, and resistant to spills, stains, kids, pets, and any smudge that comes your way. And when the unavoidable “oops” happens during a lively cocktail party or slime-making session, you can breathe a sigh of relief: when the party’s over, simply roll up your rug and run it through the washing machine!
Made from sustainably-sourced premium hand-made wool, our washable rugs help define what it means to live your best life at home. Enjoying your space worry- and stress-free – we’ve got your floors covered.

Make the Most of Your Washable Wool Rug
Easy to set up: When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made in one piece, with no separate backing.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.
Add a rug pad: If you want to add a more plush feel underfoot and anchor the rug to the floor, layer a Rugs USA rug pad underneath the rug.
Cleans easily: Vacuum carefully with the brush on its highest setting. Machine wash the rug in cold water and a gentle cycle. Do not use bleach. Low tumble dry. Never wring. Wash only periodically to help prevent shredding of fibers. Low heat iron when need.

Not only are they undeniably plush and beautiful, with a soft and substantial pile that invites you to slip off your shoes and relax—they are made in one piece, and resistant to spills, stains, kids, pets, and any smudge that comes your way. And when the unavoidable “oops” happens during a lively cocktail party or slime-making session, you can breathe a sigh of relief: when the party’s over, simply roll up your rug and run it through the washing machine!
Made from sustainably-sourced premium hand-made wool, our washable rugs help define what it means to live your best life at home. Enjoying your space worry- and stress-free – we’ve got your floors covered.

Make the Most of Your Washable Wool Rug
Easy to set up: When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made in one piece, with no separate backing.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.
Add a rug pad: If you want to add a more plush feel underfoot and anchor the rug to the floor, layer a Rugs USA rug pad underneath the rug.
Cleans easily: Vacuum carefully with the brush on its highest setting. Machine wash the rug in cold water and a gentle cycle. Do not use bleach. Low tumble dry. Never wring. Wash only periodically to help prevent shredding of fibers. Low heat iron when need.

Make the Most of Your Washable Wool Rug
Easy to set up: When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made in one piece, with no separate backing.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.

Cleans easily: Vacuum carefully with the brush on its highest setting. Machine wash the rug in cold water and a gentle cycle. Do not use bleach. Low tumble dry. Never wring. Wash only periodically to help prevent shredding of fibers. Low heat iron when need.

long_description:
Rugs are at the heart of your home, where all the action happens. The occasional "oops" is a fact of life; and lucky for all of us, cleaning our rugs just got much easier. Say hello to the Rugs USA Washable Rugs Collection!
One-piece design: Our washable rugs have an integrated non-slip backing, which eliminates the hassle of needing a separate backing layer. When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made from sustainably-sourced premium synthetic fibers, our machine-washable rugs help you feel good with every step.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.
Add a rug pad: Want a plusher feel underfoot? Simply layer a Rugs USA rug pad underneath the rug for extra cushioning.
Launders easily: To clean, machine wash with cold water. Do not use bleach. We recommend line drying or drying without heat on an air-only dryer cycle. A low heat iron can be used if needed.

long_description:
Rugs are at the heart of your home, where all the action happens. The occasional "oops" is a fact of life; and lucky for all of us, cleaning our rugs just got much easier. Say hello to the Rugs USA Washable Rugs Collection!
One-piece design: Our washable rugs have an integrated non-slip backing, which eliminates the hassle of needing a separate backing layer. When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made from sustainably-sourced premium synthetic fibers, our machine-washable rugs help you feel good with every step.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.
Add a rug pad: Want a plusher feel underfoot? Simply layer a Rugs USA rug pad underneath the rug for extra cushioning.
Launders easily: To clean, machine wash with cold water. Do not use bleach. We recommend line drying or drying without heat on an air-only dryer cycle. A low heat iron can be used if needed.

name: Dolores Washable Wool
long_description:
Luxurious, machine-washable, and made by hand, Rugs USA’s Washable Wool rugs are poised to take center stage in your home. Not only are they undeniably plush and beautiful, with a soft and substantial pile that invites you to slip off your shoes and relax—they are made in one piece, and resistant to spills, stains, kids, pets, and any smudge that comes your way. And when the unavoidable “oops” happens during a lively cocktail party or slime-making session, you can breathe a sigh of relief: when the party’s over, simply roll up your rug and run it through the washing machine!
Made from sustainably-sourced premium hand-made wool, our washable rugs help define what it means to live your best life at home. Enjoying your space worry- and stress-free – we’ve got your floors covered.

Make the Most of Your Washable Wool Rug
Easy to set up: When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made in one piece, with no separate backing.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.
Add a rug pad: If you want to add a more plush feel underfoot and anchor the rug to the floor, layer a Rugs USA rug pad underneath the rug.
Cleans easily: Vacuum carefully with the brush on its highest setting. Machine wash the rug in cold water and a gentle cycle. Do not use bleach. Low tumble dry. Never wring. Wash only periodically to help prevent shredding of fibers. Low heat iron when need.

long_description:
Rugs are at the heart of your home, where all the action happens. The occasional "oops" is a fact of life; and lucky for all of us, cleaning our rugs just got much easier. Say hello to the Rugs USA Washable Rugs Collection!
One-piece design: Our washable rugs have an integrated non-slip backing, which eliminates the hassle of needing a separate backing layer. When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made from sustainably-sourced premium synthetic fibers, our machine-washable rugs help you feel good with every step.

Launders easily: To clean, machine wash with cold water. Do not use bleach. We recommend line drying or drying without heat on an air-only dryer cycle. A low heat iron can be used if needed.

Rugs are at the heart of your home, where all the action happens. The occasional "oops" is a fact of life; and lucky for all of us, cleaning our rugs just got much easier. Say hello to the Rugs USA Washable Rugs Collection!
One-piece design: Our washable rugs have an integrated non-slip backing, which eliminates the hassle of needing a separate backing layer. When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made from sustainably-sourced premium synthetic fibers, our machine-washable rugs help you feel good with every step.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.
Add a rug pad: Want a plusher feel underfoot? Simply layer a Rugs USA rug pad underneath the rug for extra cushioning.
Launders easily: To clean, machine wash with cold water. Do not use bleach. We recommend line drying or drying without heat on an air-only dryer cycle. A low heat iron can be used if needed.

name: Gizelle Washable Aztec
long_description:
Rugs are at the heart of your home, where all the action happens. The occasional "oops" is a fact of life; and lucky for all of us, cleaning our rugs just got much easier. Say hello to the Rugs USA Washable Rugs Collection!
One-piece design: Our washable rugs have an integrated non-slip backing, which eliminates the hassle of needing a separate backing layer. When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made from sustainably-sourced premium synthetic fibers, our machine-washable rugs help you feel good with every step.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.
Add a rug pad: Want a plusher feel underfoot? Simply layer a Rugs USA rug pad underneath the rug for extra cushioning.
Launders easily: To clean, machine wash with cold water. Do not use bleach. We recommend line drying or drying without heat on an air-only dryer cycle. A low heat iron can be used if needed.

name: Nancy Southwestern Diamond Washable
long_description:
Rugs are at the heart of your home, where all the action happens. The occasional "oops" is a fact of life; and lucky for all of us, cleaning our rugs just got much easier. Say hello to the Rugs USA Washable Rugs Collection!
One-piece design: Our washable rugs have an integrated non-slip backing, which eliminates the hassle of needing a separate backing layer. When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made from sustainably-sourced premium synthetic fibers, our machine-washable rugs help you feel good with every step.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.
Add a rug pad: Want a plusher feel underfoot? Simply layer a Rugs USA rug pad underneath the rug for extra cushioning.
Launders easily: To clean, machine wash with cold water. Do not use bleach. We recommend line drying or drying without heat on an air-only dryer cycle. A low heat iron can be used if needed.

name: Greta Scandinavia Diamond Washable
long_description:
Rugs are at the heart of your home, where all the action happens. The occasional "oops" is a fact of life; and lucky for all of us, cleaning our rugs just got much easier. Say hello to the Rugs USA Washable Rugs Collection!
One-piece design: Our washable rugs have an integrated non-slip backing, which eliminates the hassle of needing a separate backing layer. When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made from sustainably-sourced premium synthetic fibers, our machine-washable rugs help you feel good with every step.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.
Add a rug pad: Want a plusher feel underfoot? Simply layer a Rugs USA rug pad underneath the rug for extra cushioning.
Launders easily: To clean, machine wash with cold water. Do not use bleach. We recommend line drying or drying without heat on an air-only dryer cycle. A low heat iron can be used if needed.

Rugs are at the heart of your home, where all the action happens. The occasional "oops" is a fact of life; and lucky for all of us, cleaning our rugs just got much easier. Say hello to the Rugs USA Washable Rugs Collection!
One-piece design: Our washable rugs have an integrated non-slip backing, which eliminates the hassle of needing a separate backing layer. When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made from sustainably-sourced premium synthetic fibers, our machine-washable rugs help you feel good with every step.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.
Add a rug pad: Want a plusher feel underfoot? Simply layer a Rugs USA rug pad underneath the rug for extra cushioning.
Launders easily: To clean, machine wash with cold water. Do not use bleach. We recommend line drying or drying without heat on an air-only dryer cycle. A low heat iron can be used if needed.

name: Vicky Banded Washable
long_description:
Rugs are at the heart of your home, where all the action happens. The occasional "oops" is a fact of life; and lucky for all of us, cleaning our rugs just got much easier. Say hello to the Rugs USA Washable Rugs Collection!
One-piece design: Our washable rugs have an integrated non-slip backing, which eliminates the hassle of needing a separate backing layer. When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made from sustainably-sourced premium synthetic fibers, our machine-washable rugs help you feel good with every step.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.
Add a rug pad: Want a plusher feel underfoot? Simply layer a Rugs USA rug pad underneath the rug for extra cushioning.
Launders easily: To clean, machine wash with cold water. Do not use bleach. We recommend line drying or drying without heat on an air-only dryer cycle. A low heat iron can be used if needed.

name: Carrie Faded Washable
long_description:
Rugs are at the heart of your home, where all the action happens. The occasional "oops" is a fact of life; and lucky for all of us, cleaning our rugs just got much easier. Say hello to the Rugs USA Washable Rugs Collection!
One-piece design: Our washable rugs have an integrated non-slip backing, which eliminates the hassle of needing a separate backing layer. When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made from sustainably-sourced premium synthetic fibers, our machine-washable rugs help you feel good with every step.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.
Add a rug pad: Want a plusher feel underfoot? Simply layer a Rugs USA rug pad underneath the rug for extra cushioning.
Launders easily: To clean, machine wash with cold water. Do not use bleach. We recommend line drying or drying without heat on an air-only dryer cycle. A low heat iron can be used if needed.

name: Tara Washable Diamond
long_description:
Rugs are at the heart of your home, where all the action happens. The occasional "oops" is a fact of life; and lucky for all of us, cleaning our rugs just got much easier. Say hello to the Rugs USA Washable Rugs Collection!
One-piece design: Our washable rugs have an integrated non-slip backing, which eliminates the hassle of needing a separate backing layer. When your rug arrives, simply lay it flat in the desired space.
Innovative construction: Made from sustainably-sourced premium synthetic fibers, our machine-washable rugs help you feel good with every step.
Hard-wearing: Spill- and stain-resistant, these rugs are perfect for those with kids and pets and will hold up in high traffic areas of your home.
Add a rug pad: Want a plusher feel underfoot? Simply layer a Rugs USA rug pad underneath the rug for extra cushioning.
Launders easily: To clean, machine wash with cold water. Do not use bleach. We recommend line drying or drying without heat on an air-only dryer cycle. A low heat iron can be used if needed.

long_description: The Hilda collection is inspired by the Scandinavian trend that is celebrated for its simplicity, warm functionality, clean lines, and understated elegance. name: TW3065
long_description: Twist rugs are the definition of simple, understated elegance. The collection features striped and solid designs in muted, soft colors. Each rug is crafted from quality wool and hand-woven in traditional dhurrie style. Dhurrie is not just a rug style, but an ancient art form practiced in India for centuries. Dhurrie rugs feature a flat, tight, durable weave with no pile, making Twist rugs ideal all-purpose rugs for any room.

For centuries the beautiful colors used by the ancient Egyptian artists to decorate the temples, monuments and homes of the nobles have been admired but never duplicated. The artists used a vast array of colors using natural ingredients and techniques that were difficult to recreate even with today's technology...until now. The Kharma collection with it's aged tea stained effect and fine heat set yarns recreate that ancient look once again. Woven of 100% Olefin.
